/>\n大執位完就變左7個.果3個執左去邊?佢地答唔到,因為睇唔到.<br />\n3個嚴重傷憑空消失,呢啲解釋唔可以接受,根本釋除唔到公眾疑慮.<br />\n公開CCTV,公開當時分類既傷者紀錄."},{"pid":"52f4d7c5537a5290903510ad52e38e98c1fae71d","tid":1562792,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:30:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">旺區兼狗竇前面搶犯？？？就算俾你搶到，去得邊呀仆街？？？！！！</span></strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>為左殤台個牌為左碗飯，童星老監馮生都要做奶共狗鳥！！！<br />\n<br />\n為紀念燒死林彬而起嘅18樓C座，狗馮既係老監亦負責主要角色，啱啱居然勁做維撚狗，幫狗政Spin話831死人只係街邊八婆鳩吹出黎，又吹香港咁大城市死幾個人點會遮得到！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嘩嘩嘩！！我愈聽愈以為轉左俾Mei西監製添！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>疑點1: </ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n光明正大點解要cap圖唔直接放片？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins><strong>疑點2: </strong></ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n點解Cap既所有圖都唔見畜聾打人，直播又會見到？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins><strong>疑點3: </strong></ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁撚簡單既事點解要封站兩日？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins><strong>疑點4: </strong></ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n連721都唔會4個部門一齊見記者，點解831會？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">我依家信太子有無辜市民被殺害了</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一句到尾啦，係支共命令&quot;止暴制亂&quot;之下，明知一日拖一日尤其頭七都唔交出足本只會愈拖愈亂，咁都唔交你地話點解呢？？？？</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">加埋依家毛EE爆料，831事件冇人死？？？<br />\n<br />\n<strong></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFYI，當晚現場傳第一消息：有人打死人，但唔係香港警察，你話係邊個呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？？？！！！</span></span></span></strong></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0d823fa44a8c13769e84bd664783476a335ee7e6","tid":1562792,"uid":5526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:31:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6d0c43c27e353671fcf1eb30857955987a10873","tid":1562792,"uid":279895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:32:45.000Z","msg":"消防係戰友<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb1848666096493d788936d7d860744d5d5262cd","tid":1562792,"uid":179414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:51:00.000Z","msg":"消防要幫狗隊執屎已經好慘，我地要繼續見到救護車同消防熱烈歡迎擁護，對狗繼續屌尻佢地，分化到啲狗繼續懷疑人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2431ecf4101d797040169f042b9623cd720722f9","tid":1562792,"uid":111007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb1848666096493d788936d7d860744d5d5262cd","tid":1562792,"uid":179414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:51:00.000Z","msg":"消防要幫狗隊執屎已經好慘，我地要繼續見到救護車同消防熱烈歡迎擁護，對狗繼續屌尻佢地，分化到啲狗繼續懷疑人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"ci